# Phase 4: Publication Coordination (Partially Complete)

## Completed
- `CoordinationMode` enum (Simple, Publication) in `flow/mod.rs`
- `PublicationStore` with Publication, Review, Grade types in `flow/publication.rs`
- Publication tools (publish, cite, review, search_publications, etc.) in `flow/pub_tools.rs`
- `CustomToolHandler` trait in `agent/mod.rs` for extensible tool handlers
- Integration of custom handlers into Agent's tool execution flow
- Flow events for publication mode (PublicationCreated, PublicationReviewed, PublicationConsensus)
- Zhipu provider streaming bug fixed (VecDeque event queue + unified `process_sse_data` helper)
- Consensus aggregation logic in flow engine:
  - PubSnapshot diffing: captures store state before/after each node, emits events
  - PublicationCreated, PublicationReviewed, PublicationConsensus events now emitted
  - `allow_self_review` threaded from coordination config to PublicationStore
  - `review_from` node field injects publications from specified nodes into agent prompt
  - Fixed hardcoded consensus threshold in pub_tools.rs (uses store.consensus_threshold())
- Publication flow tested end-to-end

## Remaining Work
- Add agent memory/evolution (self-editing prompts)
- Citation tracking between agent outputs

---

# Tmux Cleanup on Shutdown

## Completed
- `TmuxManager::cleanup_all_sessions()` returns `Vec<String>` (session names)
- Shutdown handler in `main.rs` displays: `Killed N tmux session(s): session1, session2, ...`
- Ctrl+C signal handler cleans up tmux sessions before exit

